measures.name: Updated
measures.expression: "Data provided by USAFacts. Because of the frequency of data upates, they may not reflect the exact numbers reported by government organizations or the news media. For more information or to download the data, please click the logo below.  Data updated through " & FORMAT([Max date],"mmmm dd, yyyy") & "."

measures.name: Drill-through button text
measures.expression: IF(SELECTEDVALUE(StateDim[State],0)==0,"Click on a State to view by County  ", "Click here to view by County in " & VALUES(StateDim[State code]) &"  ")

measures.name: Methodology
expression: "This interactive feature aggregates data from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC), state- and local-level public health agencies. County-level data is confirmed by referencing state and local agencies directly.

measures.name: Notes
expression: "New York* covers 5 counties (Bronx, Kings, New York, Queens, Richmond), not New York county.
City of St. Louis was renamed to St. Louis City.
City and Borough of Juneau was renamed to Juneau Borough.
Municipality of Anchorage was renamed to Anchorage.
Jackson County includes other portions of Kansas City.
